trictions may not be used to store or transmit prohibited restricted and confidential data as defined by the stanford university information security office support it services supports the exchange mailbox service on a 24 7 basis support includes setup and management of the exchange mailbox servers and mailboxes supported protocols for accessing exchange email mailbox pops and imaps mapi outlook on campus outlook anywhere outlook from off campus web https and webdav rates the exchange mailbox service is available to faculty staff and students for a monthly fee the rates are published on the computing services rates page getting started submit requests for exchange email service via orderit or by calling 5 help 650 725 4357 last modified mon 24 oct 2011 at 17 22 pages about this service overview roles and responsibilities actions order service find answers submit a helpsu request stanford answers related pages email footer links stanford university helpsu user login stanford university terms of use copyright complaints
